Kwesinye isigaba sesiQephu, kucacisiwe ukuthi i-Stardust izobeka irekhodi elisha ngokuba indizamshini esheshayo ukubuya emhlabeni, iphule irekhodi elabekwa ngo-May 1969 ngesikhathi sokubuya kuka-Apollo X. Lokhu kusho ukuthi irekhodi elisho izinga lokushesha kokubuya emhlabeni leli elizobekwa yi-Stardust. Ngakho-ke, impendulo efanele yale mibuzo ekubonisa ukuthi irekhodi lizobekwa kuphi ngukuthi irekhodi lokubuyela emhlabeni ngokushesha.

Izinketho:

[1] "Ukukhanyise ububanzi besibhaka bhaka" - lokhu akukhulunywanga ngokusebenzisa irekhodi;
[2] "Ukubonakala emadholobheni athile" - yize kubonakala, ayikhulumi nge-rekhodi;
[3] "Ukubuyela emhlabeni ngokushesha" - lokhu kuyahambisana nencazelo ethi irekhodi lizobekwa ngokushesha ekubuyeni emhlabeni;
[4] "Ukuhamba ngokushesha okukhulu ukusuka eSan Francisco ukuya eLos Angeles" - kushiwo isivinini kodwa ayisho irekhodi elizobekwa.

Ngakho-ke, impendulo enembile ngesihloko sekhulu ukuthi irekhodi leStardust lizobeka "ukubuyela emhlabeni ngokushesha".

Isigaba esiqokomisa indawo yaseMontevideo sisho ukuthi isendaweni eseningizimu yeNkabazwe futhi esezindaweni eziseduze namatropiki. Ngamagama alelo ndaba, ihlobo eMontevideo libe nesilinganiso sokushisa esiphezulu, cishe ngaphezu kuka-30°C, okusho ukuthi izimo sezulu azipholile ngalelo xesha. Ubusika, ngokuphambene nalokho, buba bufudumele kakhulu futhi binomswakama, okwenza isimo sezulu sibandayo kakhulu. Umbuzo ubuza ukuthi isivakashi kufanele sivakashele iMontevideo yini uma sifuna izimo sezulu ezipholile. Ngokwemibhalo, izimo sezulu ezipholile zikhona ngesikhathi sasebusika eMontevideo. Kodwa-ke, eMontevideo asikho isikhawu esiqondile sezulu esibizwa ngokuthi yizimvula noma ubusika njengoba izinga lemvula lihlala lilingana unyaka wonke. Ngokusho kwemisho ethi "IMontevideo isezindaweni eseduze namatropiki; ngezinyanga zasehlobo, amazinga okushisa angaphezu kuka-+30°C avamile", kanye "Ubusika bungaba nzima kakhulu," kusobala ukuthi izimo sezulu ezipholile zitholakala ngesikhathi sasebusika eMontevideo, okuyisikhathi esiphikisana nelingxenye esenyakatho yezwe lapho kubuswa ubusika. Ngakho-ke, impendulo ethi "Uma kuyisebusika Enyakatho Yezwe" ayifanele ngoba isimo sezulu esibandayo eMontevideo siba ngesikhathi sobusika bayo (eningizimu), okuphambene nesimo sempumalanga (enyakatho). Impendulo efanele kuyoba "Lapho kuyisebusika eMontevideo," kodwa leyo ayikho ngqo ezinketho, ngakho impendulo eduze kakhulu neholiwe komusho ukuthi "Lapho kuyisehlobo eMontevideo" ayinembile ngoba ihlobo lisho izinga lokushisa eliphezulu kakhulu. Ngakho-ke akekho opsi ofanele ngokucacile ngaphandle kokuthi uma sibheka unyaka wonke, izimo zikhulu zibandayo ngesikhathi sobusika eMontevideo, okuyinto eqondile yesimo sezulu esipholile esikhuluma ngaso kulo mbhalo.

Izinketho ezinikeziwe ziyaziwa:

[1] «Lapho kuyisehlobo eMontevideo» – ihlobo lithatha isikhundla sokuqalisa isimo sezulu esifudumele;
[2] «Uma kuyisehlobo Enyakatho Yezwe» – akukhulunywanga ukuthi isivakashi kumele sivele eNyakatho yezwe;
[3] «Uma kuyisikhathi sezimvula eMontevideo» – umbhalo uthi azikho izikhawu eziqondile zesikhathi sezimvula;
[4] «Uma kuyisebusika Enyakatho Yezwe» – akuvumelani ngesikhathi sobusika eMontevideo.

Ngokubhekelela lokhu, akukho okuqondile kunazo zonke, kodwa impendulo engcono kakhulu iya ku-1 ngoba imibandela yesicelo sombuzo isithi nkcukacha zomkhathi ezipholile, kusho ukuthi kufanele kuvakashelwe eMontevideo lapho kwenzeka izimo sezulu ezipholile, okuyilapho kungase kube ubusika, bese izinketho 2 no-4 azihambisi ngqo neMontevideo. Ngakho impendulo efanelekile kakhulu ngokwesimo esifanele kungaba ukwazi ukuthi isivakashi sifuna ukuphola kanti iMontevideo iba nezipholile ngesikhathi sobusika sayo eseningizimu. Kodwa ngenxa yokungabikho kokukhetha okuphelele, impendulo eduze kakhulu iya ku-1.
